quran[40]{c,v,t}:
  19,59,"Nuko baje gukurikirwa n’abandi bantu baretse gusali, bakurikira ibyo bararikira. Abo bazahura n’ukorama guhambaye"
  19,60,"Uretse abazicuza, bakemera Allah ndetse bakanakora ibikorwa byiza; abo bazinjira mu Ijuru kandi ntibazahuguzwa na gato"
  19,61,"(Bazinjira) mu busitani buhoraho, (Allah) Nyirimpuhwe yasezeranyije abagaragu be (bemeye ibyo) batabonye. Mu by’ukuri isezerano rye rizasohora nta kabuza"
  19,62,(Mu ijuru) ntibazigera bumvamo amagambo adafite umumaro; uretse (kumva) indamutso y’amahoro (Salamu). Kandi bazaba bafitemo amafunguro mu gitondo na nimugoroba
  19,63,Iryo ni ryo juru tuzaha abagaragu bacu bagandukira (Allah) ngo barizungure
  19,64,"Kandi (twe abamalayika) ntitujya tumanuka bitari ku itegeko rya Nyagasani wawe (yewe Muhamadi). Ni We ugenga ibiri imbere yacu, ibiri inyuma yacu ndetse no hagati yabyo ubwabyo; kandi Nyagasani wawe ntajya yibagirwa"
  19,65,"Nyagasani w’ibirere n’isi n’ibiri hagati yabyo. Bityo, jya umugaragira (wenyine) kandi ujye uhozaho kumugaragira (kabone n’iyo byaba bikugoye). Ese hari uwo waba uzi witiranwa na we"
  19,66,"Kandi umuntu (w’umuhakanyi) aravuga ati “Ese nindamuka mpfuye, nzazurwa mbe muzima?”"
  19,67,"Ese umuntu ntiyibuka ko mbere y’ibyo, ari twe twamuremye kandi nta cyo yari cyo"
  19,68,"Ndahiye kuri Nyagasani wawe! Rwose tuzabakoranya (abahakana izuka) hamwe n’amashitani, hanyuma tubazane ku nkengero z’umuriro wa Jahanamu bapfukamye"
  19,69,Hanyuma rwose muri buri gatsiko tuzakuremo abarushije abandi kwigomeka kuri (Allah) Nyirimpuhwe (babe ari bo babanza guhanwa)
  19,70,Hanyuma mu by’ukuri ni twe tuzi neza abakwiye gutwikirwa mu muriro kurusha abandi
  19,71,Nta n’umwe muri mwe utazayinyuraho (Siratwa); iryo ni ihame ntakuka rya Nyagasani wawe
  19,72,"Hanyuma tuzarokore ba bandi batinye (Allah, bayinyureho), maze tureke inkozi z’ibibi (zigwe mu muriro) zipfukamye"
  19,73,"N’iyo (abantu) basomewe amagambo yacu asobanutse, abahakanye babwira abemeye bati “Ese ni irihe tsinda muri aya yombi (abahakanye n’abemeye) rihagaze neza kurusha irindi rikaba rinarimo abantu beza?”"
  19,74,"None se ni ibisekuru bingahe twarimbuye mbere yabo (abahakanyi bo ku gihe cy’Intumwa Muhamadi), byabarushaga ubutunzi no kugaragara neza"
  19,75,"Vuga (yewe Muhamadi) uti “Umuntu uri mu buyobe, (Allah) Nyirimpuhwe azamwongerera igihe (cyo gukomeza kuba muri ubwo buyobe) kugeza ubwo bazabona ibyo basezeranyijwe, byaba ibihano (ku isi) cyangwa imperuka. Ubwo ni bwo bazamenya ufite umwanya mubi (ubuturo bubi) cyane n’ufite ingabo z’inyantege nke.”"
  19,76,Kandi Allah yongerera kuyoboka ba bandi bayobotse. Naho ibikorwa byiza bihoraho ni byo bitanga ingororano n’iherezo ryiza kwa Nyagasani wawe
  19,77,"Ese wabonye wa wundi wahakanye amagambo yacu, maze akavuga ati “Rwose (ku munsi w’imperuka) nzahabwa imitungo n’urubyaro?”"
  19,78,Ese yaba yaramenye ibyihishe (akabona ko azahabwa imitungo n’urubyaro)? Cyangwa yagiranye isezerano na (Allah) Nyirimpuhwe (ry’uko azabihabwa)
  19,79,"Si ko bimeze! Ahubwo tuzandika ibyo avuga, maze tuzamwongerere ibihano"
  19,80,"Kandi tuzamuzungura ibyo avuga (imitungo n’urubyaro), maze atugereho ari wenyine"
  19,81,"Banishyiriyeho ibigirwamana (barabisenga) baretse Allah, kugira ngo bibarinde (ibihano bya Allah) kandi bibaheshe icyubahiro"
  19,82,"Si ko bimeze! Ahubwo (ibyo bigirwamana) bizihakana uko kubisenga kwabo, maze bibabere abanzi (ku munsi w’imperuka)"
  19,83,"Ese ntubona ko twoherereje abahakanyi amashitani, kugira ngo abashishikarize kwigomeka"
  19,84,"Bityo, ntugire ubwira (bwo gushaka ko bahanwa), kuko mu by’ukuri tubabarira iminsi ntarengwa"
  19,85,"Umunsi tuzakoranya abagandukira (Allah), berekeza kwa (Allah) Nyirimpuhwe, bameze nk’abashyitsi b’imena"
  19,86,"Tukanashorera inkozi z’ibibi tuziganisha mu muriro wa Jahanamu, zishwe n’inyota"
  19,87,"Ntibazagira ubushobozi bwo kugira uwo bakorera ubuvugizi, uretse uzaba afite isezerano rya (Allah) Nyirimpuhwe (ryo gukora ubwo buvugizi)"
  19,88,(Abahakanyi) baranavuze bati “(Allah) Nyirimpuhwe afite umwana!”
  19,89,Rwose ibyo muvuga ni amahano
  19,90,"Ibirere biba byenda gusandara, n’isi yenda gusatagurika, ndetse n’imisozi yenda kuriduka"
  19,91,Kubera ko bavuze ko (Allah) Nyirimpuhwe afite umwana
  19,92,Kandi bidakwiye ko (Allah) Nyirimpuhwe yagira umwana
  19,93,Nta na kimwe mu biri mu birere no ku isi kizagera imbere ya (Allah) Nyirimpuhwe kitari umugaragu (uciye bugufi)
  19,94,Mu by’ukuri (Allah) arabazi neza kandi yaranababaruye nyabyo
  19,95,"Kandi ku munsi w’izuka, buri wese azamugana ari wenyine (nta buvugizi, nta n’icyo yitwaje)"
  19,96,"Mu by’ukuri abemeye bakanakora ibyiza, (Allah) Nyirimpuhwe azabahundagazaho urukundo rwe, (anabahe gukundwa n’abagaragu be)"
  19,97,"Mu by’ukuri (Qur’an) twayoroheje gusobanuka mu rurimi rwawe (yewe Muhamadi) kugira ngo uyikoreshe ugeza inkuru nziza ku bagandukira (Allah), ndetse unayikoreshe uburira abantu (b’abahakanyi) bagira izima"
  19,98,None se ni ibisekuru bingahe twarimbuye mbere yabo! Ese hari n’umwe muri bo ukibona cyangwa ngo wumve akoma